About

dScryb is an award-winning tabletop roleplaying game publisher of lush descriptions, immersive sounds and interactive maps: Looking for a killer narrative of a nearby goblin patrol? We've got you covered. Perhaps your session calls for the thrilling music and ambience of an epic vault heist? You'll find that as well. Is your party looking for its next quest at the Adventurer's Guildhall? Here's the map and key.

Let dScryb’s team of talented writers, composers, and illustrators free your creative energy and time for all the other aspects of planning and running the perfect campaign.

Copyright © 2025 dScryb. All Rights Reserved.

dScryb is not affiliated with Wizards of the Coast. Click here to learn more.
